headline: ETH Under $2,500: Friday Sees Highest Outflows From Spot ETH ETFs This Month
summary: Ether bounces from intraday lows after a sharp 7.25% swing; 24-hour trading volume surged nearly 19% above the 7-day average, signaling heightened market activity.
